        </div>

        <div class="content-container">
          <div class="full-width-content">
            <p>We stock common OEM Miele stove parts for same-day repairs, including:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] flex items-center gap-2  no-bullet pl-1">
                <span><strong>Heating elements</strong></span>
              </li>
              <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-1">
                <span><strong>Igniters and spark modules</strong></span>
              </li>
              <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-1">
                <span><strong>Burner heads and caps</strong></span>
              </li>
              <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-1">
                <span><strong>Temperature sensors and thermostats</strong></span>
              </li>
              <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-1">
                <span><strong>Control knobs and touch panels</strong></span>
              </li>
              <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-1">
                <span><strong>Electronic control boards</strong></span>
              </li>
              <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-1">
                <span><strong>Convection motors and fans</strong></span>
              </li>
              <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-1">
                <span><strong>Gas regulators and safety valves</strong></span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p style="margin-top: 20px;">We only use <strong>genuine Miele replacement parts</strong> to ensure the highest quality, safety, and performance.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="page-container" id="anchor-5">
        <div class="header-container">
          <div class="head-content-h">
            <h2>Should You Repair or Replace Your Miele Stove?</h2>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-container">
          <div class="full-width-content">
            <p>We provide brand-specific, honest advice:</p>
            <ul style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
              <li><strong>Repair</strong> – If the unit is under 20 years old, in otherwise good condition, and repair costs are less than half the cost of replacement</li>
              <li><strong>Replace</strong> – If it's significantly aged, has multiple system failures, or requires rare/obsolete parts</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Typical Repair Costs</h3>
            <p>Your service includes:</p>

            <ul class="space-y-4">
                <li class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border-l-4 border-[#ca0913] flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-1">Licensed, factory-trained Miele specialists</li>
